7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Longshot AI and Simplified share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form, Templates, Tone Control. Where Longshot AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Plagiarism Check, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Simplified uniquely offers Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Longshot AI holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Simplified scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Simplified comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Longshot AI begins at $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Longshot AI's free tier and Simplified's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
