b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Longshot AI is best suited for fact checked content, SEO articles, blog posts, research heavy writing, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Simplified, meanwhile, shines for social media content, graphic design, small businesses, marketing teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2021, Longshot AI describes itself as \"AI writing tool with built-in fact-checking and citations.\" Simplified, established in 2020, positions itself as \"All-in-one AI platform for writing, design, and social media.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Longshot AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (7 vs 6), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Simplified is a poor choice — far from it. Simplified excels in its own right, particularly for social media content and graphic design.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value unique fact-checking and citation features, go with Longshot AI. If combines writing, design, video, and social media management matters more to you, Simplified is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
